We will use remote reading for the new meter, which usually works without any particular actions. However, in some cases, for example if the meter is placed in a steel cabinet, we might need to mount a radio antenna by the cabinet to enable the remote Reading.
Wixii Faahfaain dheeraad aha fadlan la xiriir
Waad Mahadsantihiin.
Korontada waa ladamin doona xilliga saacadda la beddalayo
Kind Regards
You will receive a new electricity meter from us. The new meter will have many functions that you will benefit from, including the possibility to follow your hourly electricity usage and to see your momentary power. If you are producing your own electricity, you will also benefit from that the new meters are prepared to measure the electricity that you want to sell.
Xaddiga isticmaalka korontada waxaa si fudud looga akhrin doonaa kumbuyuutar.
Koronto la’aan ayay guryuhu ahaanayaan xilliga saacadda la beddalayo. Inta saacadda la beddalayo waxey qaadane ku dhawaad 10 daqiiqo.
Your house or apartment will not have any electricity during the exchange of the meter. However, the exchange takes approximately 10 minutes, so the time without electricity will not be long.
Saacaddu waa in ey ku xidhantahay meel la gaari karo, qofka shaqada qabanayana haysto meel ku filan oo uu shaqadiisa ku qabsan karo,sidaa daraadeed ka hor leexi wixii caqabad ku ah in shaqadaa la qabto.
AB Borlänge Energi Elnät
Our contractor Hydrostandard Mätteknik Nordic AB will perform the replacement and in the information letter in Swedish we state the period for when we will replace the meters in your area. Information will also be posted in the stairwell of your building. In apartment buildings, the meter is placed outside your apartment and therefore you do not need to be present when we exchange the meter.
